title: Reverted back to Java 7
message:
Reverted back to Java 7

Java 8 support for Android is rather unstable at the moment.
The Jack compiler is deprecated and the default toolchain
requires dependencies marked as alpha.

Since this app currently only used lambdas as a Java 8 feature,
these have been removed for now.

title: Fixed calculation of duration < 48 hours (fixes #10)
message:
Fixed calculation of duration < 48 hours (fixes #10)

If an item was lent two days ago, but not 48 hours,
the duration displayed was "Yesterday". This fix has
been secured by unit tests.
